{"tid":1149311,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"Volkswagen 電動車登場","createTime":"2019-05-11T05:15:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-12T17:10:48.000Z","uid":160973,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"34926a4bfc496214d0d082168796a45c486be1ab","tid":1149311,"uid":160973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-11T05:15:45.000Z","msg":"Volkswagen第一部ID系列電動車ID.3在歐洲開始接受訂單，其體積跟VW Golf相若，續航距離330公里，終於又有部似樣少少嘅電動車啦，不過喺外國揸如果多叉電位都係唔錯嘅。<br />\n<br />\n仲要只係將於2019年尾投產，2020年中開始交車，當中有30,000部為特別版Launch Edition，屬中電版本，即擁有420公里續航力（WLTP），價錢就同 Golf 差唔多，歐洲賣緊 270K EUR，大約 25 萬港幣左右。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2LCpwfJ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2LCpwfJ&d=0%2BTJGVp%2BJnQ%2Fy6oFhB9FUD2x7fSflbdxuct7bsFM5Qs%3D&h=f05c6484\" target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2LCpwfJ</a>"},{"pid":"4ffbbab949e93eb34770d75b8e677cb4a417f592","tid":1149311,"uid":35864,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-11T05:19:36.000Z","msg":"後座無窗？"},{"pid":"7429cd5ab55ec5542a82b8e90a6551cee02779fc","tid":1149311,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-11T08:50:26.000Z","msg":"即係唔會再有eGolf<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d13ba0962e9d68aec4518bff0ed205e8b135582","tid":1149311,"uid":201777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-11T09:54:40.000Z","msg":"飛機杯。"},{"pid":"3ebb922861c0798181e56e1b3ef1d51d044248a6","tid":1149311,"uid":1748,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-11T09:58:06.000Z","msg":"7到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8aaecb34682ba13b372b19c361771c68c1f6eb24","tid":1149311,"uid":26536,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-11T09:59:05.000Z","msg":"大電好似話都係30另萬<br />\n勁吸引...又後驅"},{"pid":"a7c1fb82fae82ba090f772ef16ed920f0f99a1e3","tid":1149311,"uid":72771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-12T15:3